analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: The GMS 49 print dictates a neutral regime where upward OGV vectors collide with credit spread decompression. Despite liquidity stability, VIX elevation and fragile sentiment mandate a tactical pivot. Monitor reflationary impulses before increasing exposure. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
